Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Our next conquest shall be the planet Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:01:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,lt is a foregone conclusion that we shall rape that fertile land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that Master Glode has ever been too discriminating...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The scent of blood is what we live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last one from Bamuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How long until the next planet fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyon is but two or three days distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Our warriors already hunger for the taste of flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed with all speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The cold feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,l told you not to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, whatever will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Neris!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, you do know what day it is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not just a splash in the pool, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's a very important ritual for your upcoming marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess' marriage should be the most auspicious of occasions,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so why do l feel such an ominous sense of foreboding?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, when all of Lyon is full of peace and joy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To Prince Zeke and Princess Flare! Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe so many people have come out to celebrate just for the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How right you are, my Flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But those assembled here are not the only ones who celebrate tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,all the land shares our joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Though our lands may be limited and our numbers few,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,our population is blessed with a beautiful green planet and pure, clean water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, the loving and caring nature of our people is well known.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,lt tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You naughty Poppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Word from the east! Everything's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Neris, take care of Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them! Burn them! Set them on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For every man you kill, there will be another woman in your bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Neris!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Neris!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,N..No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lay one slimy tentacle on my princess and l'll kill you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Y..You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never touch my princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Neris!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Re..Release me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Such spirit. You might even survive the pleasures l have planned for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And if l'm still alive at the end, will you spare my princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,lf you can outlast me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider it a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Neris...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Neris...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Neris...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised not to touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,St... Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For this, you shall die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,lt may seem as though l've lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but l still accomplished my primary goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My goal... my...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess! Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess! Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zeke, the princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,l failed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,lt isn't your fault, Neris.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is collapsing. We must leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:21:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,lt's over, we've lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true, Neris.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.30,0:22:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,l wonder if everything is like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When a whole planet has been raped,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,nature's wrath can be brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.42,0:23:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.70,0:23:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.23,0:23:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeke?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeke...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.28,0:24:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body warms me so...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.32,0:24:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can the beauty that was Lyon ever be restored?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.36,0:24:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! Of course it will be reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.16,0:25:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As it was in the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.23,0:25:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it shall be again!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.09,0:25:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}l believe that even the saddest dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.73,0:25:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are like the clouds up in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.27,0:25:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.50,0:25:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like the tails of a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.31,0:25:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whispering as they go by
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.51,0:25:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When l can tie a ribbon in my hair
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.15,0:25:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A ribbon made of light
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.72,0:26:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then l can promise
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.92,0:26:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}l'll love you forever
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.86,0:26:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forever is a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.63,0:26:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do it to me harder
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.30,0:26:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take me again roughly
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.90,0:26:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will it be long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.58,0:26:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For my love?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.21,0:26:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, place it against my cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.79,0:26:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}l'll hold it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.95,0:26:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So gently
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.82,0:26:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}l will hold
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.23,0:26:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.46,0:26:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deep inside my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.57,0:26:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gather up all the pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.20,0:26:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of my scattered tears
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.34,0:26:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some day
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.54,0:26:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some way
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.75,0:27:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}l will be happy too
